From: "Dr. Oscar Pedro Larghi" <oplarghi@pinos.com>

There is no indication of whether the cat was rabid. If rabies was
disgnosed, Brazil's Ministry of Health norms coincide with recommendations
of the WHO Expert Committee on Rabies.
Heterologous serum, which is most likely used in Estado do Acre, Brazil, by
itself could cause urticariform reactions.
